{"tid":436943,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"廢柴ielts操writing","createTime":"2017-10-15T14:12:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T23:48:01.000Z","uid":15377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"db38ef6d4284a9d6b69a82216061cfeef490c015","tid":436943,"uid":15377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T14:12:56.000Z","msg":"我想咁多位 ielts寫作可以點操 真心好無助 <br />\n加上自己又無底 <br />\n有時睇見條題目都唔知點寫 或者 諗到點寫或寫唔出<br />\n想問下有無咩書可以值得買黎睇下 或者 有咩心得可以好快咁善自己嘅writing<br />\nAim 6.5<br />\nDse writing 3 overall 3<br />\n求咁多位指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16e8608888b39529b3995c5852f3bf6b3958dac5","tid":436943,"uid":141189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T14:28:28.000Z","msg":"最好睇多d範文 你會發現ielts對paraphrasing 有特別嘅執著 你要學識點去用唔同嘅寫法去表達同一個意思 <br />\n可以試下cambridge ielts book 5 起手"},{"pid":"d54b5d47376c4742adf359169270d70b52474c42","tid":436943,"uid":152556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T14:35:02.000Z","msg":"有框架 例如題目係兩邊opinions 就一段intro 兩邊意見各一段再ending 就算文筆唔好睇落都靚仔D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce272f7b293d4cb7fed818bcc5938abc58f66cf","tid":436943,"uid":15377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T14:40:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有框架 例如題目係兩邊opinions 就一段intro 兩邊意見各一段再ending 就算文筆唔好睇落都靚仔D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 巴打係咪講緊利大於弊個d題<br />\n如果我一段intro<br />\n2段支持自己嘅觀點<br />\n一段conclusion<br />\n咁寫又得唔得"},{"pid":"235abd4d01ac802e24be5454ac2a8e2b9b9c72ce","tid":436943,"uid":15377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T14:41:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最好睇多d範文 你會發現ielts對paraphrasing 有特別嘅執著 你要學識點去用唔同嘅寫法去表達同一個意思 <br />\n可以試下cambridge ielts book 5 起手</blockquote><br />\n我做緊cambridge ielts book12"},{"pid":"760dde8b0aa58c2ea37afaf799078dbd4dbd5c6e","tid":436943,"uid":15377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T14:42:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最好睇多d範文 你會發現ielts對paraphrasing 有特別嘅執著 你要學識點去用唔同嘅寫法去表達同一個意思 <br />\n可以試下cambridge ielts book 5 起手</blockquote><br />\n我做緊cambridge ielts book12</blockquote><br />\n佢入面d範文通常都係得5-6分嘅student sample <br />\n所以諗住買d書睇下 有咩方法改下d作文"},{"pid":"59365d1ed693ec3b62ca113a6a8dceb0d4b94c92","tid":436943,"uid":153994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T14:45:05.000Z","msg":"買 Ielts Write Right<br />\n有好多範文 仲有好多vocab同埋罐頭句比你背<br />\npart1&amp;2都要留意成篇文個structure<br />\n<br />\n利申 試過part2內容有離題但靠vocab同structure都去到6"},{"pid":"18cc3323e3f982c100732ef45c66c0d3eef830a6","tid":436943,"uid":153994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T14:46:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有框架 例如題目係兩邊opinions 就一段intro 兩邊意見各一段再ending 就算文筆唔好睇落都靚仔D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 巴打係咪講緊利大於弊個d題<br />\n如果我一段intro<br />\n2段支持自己嘅觀點<br />\n一段conclusion<br />\n咁寫又得唔得</blockquote><br />\n留意要加番個駁論 篇文會靚啲"},{"pid":"453c08b713f2deb1ca6068462f81459c76e3be86","tid":436943,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T14:54:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f2ee9a540689e18323406aa8c5059cca7b004f0","tid":436943,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T15:05:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14eba8664036d8dd9748575f9d9a1e1fd5098c43","tid":436943,"uid":84148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T15:07:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最好睇多d範文 你會發現ielts對paraphrasing 有特別嘅執著 你要學識點去用唔同嘅寫法去表達同一個意思 <br />\n可以試下cambridge ielts book 5 起手</blockquote><br />\n絕對認同，我task 1狂paraphrase,task 2唔夠時間寫左100字都6.5.  利申祼考"},{"pid":"7427fe3fd9a0b017b2b9bd8bbf21e50d38e88eb8","tid":436943,"uid":15377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T15:09:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最好睇多d範文 你會發現ielts對paraphrasing 有特別嘅執著 你要學識點去用唔同嘅寫法去表達同一個意思 <br />\n可以試下cambridge ielts book 5 起手</blockquote><br />\n絕對認同，我task 1狂paraphrase,task 2唔夠時間寫左100字都6.5.  利申祼考</blockquote><br />\n咁癲 唔係話唔夠字會扣分咩 你咁都有6.5 你task1咪寫得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e706ceb2be6e61eb8ba3e665f5a9ac5bd9e4632","tid":436943,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T15:12:27.000Z","msg":"操reading同writing既回報係大大超過writing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec21d6924eb98a503f55bb6ca9038d587552271f","tid":436943,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T15:18:59.000Z","msg":"ielts只可以靠熟<br />\n<br />\n6.5-7 呢個人位大致係dse 4左右"},{"pid":"e6f4298be00233a5a4fa438bb6109245f1188adb","tid":436943,"uid":15377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:18:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>操reading同writing既回報係大大超過writing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我知 但係呢份卷低分都會拉低好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d209eb1aebea3b8fb5214cc5245855fae227e04f","tid":436943,"uid":77496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:34:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>操reading同writing既回報係大大超過writing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71fecfbd7f593ba7aabe57d07068586614710b79","tid":436943,"uid":109198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:39:54.000Z","msg":"都係好似上面巴打咁講<br />\n睇下啲範文學佢點樣分段 學佢用既框架去令你篇文 organised<br />\n我個陣就兩篇都分四段<br />\n仲有記得ielts好著重你sentence structure ,盡量避免長加complex嘅句子，因為易出錯，唔好弄巧成拙，用簡單嘅短句表達到你想講咩就得"},{"pid":"43d07fc1f7c7c0cbad18460077765db94d77e1c3","tid":436943,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:08:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04fceb388e233253c9ea1050e6ed504bc7787e7c","tid":436943,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:12:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d462c1c9a1c8e09e6960bc8e1b8ad0f625d25acf","tid":436943,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T01:56:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>操reading同<span style=\"color: red;\">listening</span>既回報係大大超過writing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f7fc470f34daba45ea4566ca2f664d03b73ff31d","tid":436943,"uid":110892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:27:54.000Z","msg":"作一篇出黎比連登仔笑下就有進步"},{"pid":"6c1234cf9667b59ad11240f8321d3ad42cc56c0c","tid":436943,"uid":152556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T06:54:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有框架 例如題目係兩邊opinions 就一段intro 兩邊意見各一段再ending 就算文筆唔好睇落都靚仔D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 巴打係咪講緊利大於弊個d題<br />\n如果我一段intro<br />\n2段支持自己嘅觀點<br />\n一段conclusion<br />\n咁寫又得唔得</blockquote><br />\n留意要加番個駁論 篇文會靚啲</blockquote><br />\n對對對"},{"pid":"95e59bec93639c3889d4f460a6f1a30cd67c2d8a","tid":436943,"uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:32:35.000Z","msg":"Cambrige IELTS Past Paper 1-10 download link<br />\n<a href=\"http://skpan.com/ls/queenays/cd871105\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fskpan.com%2Fls%2Fqueenays%2Fcd871105&d=LM5rG00v288dm81xUiMTlpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=1849c403\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://skpan.com/ls/queenays/cd871105</a>"},{"pid":"e280a1d3db414629566cd2bdd42c99a2f7fd965e","tid":436943,"uid":5377